A Jquery Plugin to handle IPad/iPhone swipes (and emulate in a browser) 

usage: $('#slides').ipad();

html structure:
<div id="slides">
  <span id="slide1" class="slide">
	slide1
  </span>
  <span id="slide2" class="slide">
	slide2
  </span>
  <span id="slide3" class="slide">
        slide3
  </span>
  <span id="slide4" class="slide">
        slide4
  </span>
</div>


